data.description: Recently updated large 3 bedroom 2.5 bath townhouse in highly desirable Farmers Branch. Conveniently located close to everything. Freshly painted throughout the home. Updated flooring in master bedroom & closet & second bathroom. Master bath has refinished cabinets with new hardware. New ceiling fan in third bedroom. New Argon-filled sliding glass doors at balcony and patio. Staircase refinished and re-stained. Garage updated with new paint. Laundry space fully updated. Large family room with vaulted ceilings. Separate wetbar area. Sunroom with access to patio. This unit has extra livable area compared to similar units in the community. Full-size washer and dryer hookups. All bedrooms located on second floor. Balcony area accessible from second bedroom. Plantation shutters upstairs. Refrigerator conveys with sale. Foundation repair completed recently with lifetime transferable warranty. Home is vacant and ready to show!
